name: Prof. Dr. x Chowdhury
about: Prof. Dr. x Chowdhury is a Child Diseased Specialist doctor in Chittagong. His qualification is MBBS, FCPS (Pediatrics), FRCP (Glasgow). He is a Professor & Head (Ex) in the Department of Pediatric at Chittagong Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Surgiscope Hospital, Chittagong. Practicing hour of Prof. Dr. Pranab Kumar Chowdhury at Surgiscope Hospital, Chittagong is 6pm to 9pm (Closed: Monday & Friday).
